            <div class="title">
                Chairman Of Ways And Means (Conduct)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1952-12-08/debates/01e53c84-8cb0-40f2-b4d1-7ccda0dcc172/Education(MiscellaneousProvisions)Money" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
