<p class="">On the last occasion? It was about 18 months ago.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-27d8200d-5309-48ae-aac9-d2f6d53e6e47" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-12-08/debates/c96a4f74-f70a-4ab5-9ad5-2af097f543fd/ChairmanOfWaysAndMeans(Conduct)#contribution-27d8200d-5309-48ae-aac9-d2f6d53e6e47">
